ShellStream - Class in com.spazedog.lib.rootfw4
Deprecated.
This class is deprecated and should no longer be used. Instead use the replacement class ShellStreamer. This class was replaced for several reasons.

For one this class has some limitations as a shell streamer in that it cannot provide constant output. It can only work as a constant input streamer.

Second this class contains some dangerous synchronized blocks. It has not provided any issues so far, but in theory it could provide a bottleneck if used across multiple threads.

Last it was not possible to fix it's issues without compromising backward compatibility. So a new class was created instead and this one will stay for an unknown period of time so not to break old code on update.
